Package: MyTradePackage
Type: Package
Title: Strategic Trade and Conflict Simulation Framework
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mario", "Filho", email = "mario.lima2002@hotmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a theoretical and computational model linking trade 
    relations, hegemonic power, and military threats. The package includes 
    analytical functions and visualization tools to explore strategic decision 
    regions in a one-dimensional political space, following the framework of 
    trade and conflict theory.
